metadata.name: NFT WORKSHOP
metadata.description:
In this workshop, you will learn the following:

ERC721 - Smart contract with your custom logic.

VS Code - Custom metadata / attributes / utilities.

Run your smart contract on the IDE & deploy on Goerli test net & test all our functions using test ETH.

View or sell your NFT on OpenSea.

BONUS:

Hashlibs VS code art / DNA Generator code.

VS Code custom logic (code) for metadata.

Links & code files shared by BYTE.

Knowledge / Time:

By the end of this short 2.5-hour class, you will have the basic understanding of how to build, code, generate art & deploy your own custom NFT project & contracts. 

When we deploy in this class, we will be using a test net, which requires test ETH we can provide to you & will show you how to obtain for your future development. 

It is as simple as one click to take your test net contract to the main net & deploy onto the ETH Blockchain to bring your NFT to the world.
